title: Zojirushi Neuro Fuzzy® Rice Cooker & Warmer NS-ZCC10/18
description:
The Neuro Fuzzy® Rice Cooker & Warmer features advanced Neuro Fuzzy® logic technology, which allows the rice cooker to 'think' for itself and make fine adjustments to temperature and heating time to cook perfect rice every time.  Available in 5-1/2 and 10 cup capacities.

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of the Zojirushi Neuro Fuzzy Rice Cooker And Warmer. Shop for the Zojirushi Neuro Fuzzy Rice Cooker And Warmer, as well as the full line of Zojirushi Kitchen Appliances at Abt today!
